---
source: cli/tests/help.rs
expression: text
---
List available properties with their descriptions for the given object

Usage: list [OPTIONS] <OBJECT>

Arguments:
  <OBJECT>
          Btrfs object path to list properties for

Options:
  -t, --type <OBJECT_TYPE>
          Object type (inode, subvol, filesystem, device)
          
          [possible values: inode, subvol, filesystem, device]

  -h, --help
          Print help
